  "title": "Personal Driver - Chauffeur (6 days / Central Region)",
  "description": "<p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Drive the Director safely and punctually to meetings, events, airports, and other destinations.</li>\n  <li>Ensure comfort, privacy, and security during all journeys.</li>\n  <li>Plan efficient routes, considering traffic and weather.</li>\n  <li>Keep the vehicle spotless, well-maintained, and serviced regularly.</li>\n  <li>Handle fueling, washing, and basic vehicle care.</li>\n  <li>Maintain discretion and professionalism at all times.</li>\n  <li>Be flexible and ready for early mornings, late evenings, weekends, or urgent trips.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Valid Class 3/3A + vocational driving licence.</li>\n  <li>Strong knowledge of Singapore roads.</li>\n  <li>Professional, well-groomed, and discreet.</li>\n  <li>Good communication skills with the ability to interact with senior executives.</li>\n  <li>Reliable, adaptable, and proactive.</li>\n  <li>Prior experience as a personal driver/chauffeur required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>Wecruit Pte Ltd</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p><br></p>",
